aku suka uang

00:24:11.030 --> 00:24:12.240
dan Tuan Song Wenchang,

00:24:12.640 --> 00:24:14.010
tapi aku tidak suka perawan tua

00:24:14.010 --> 00:24:14.450
seperti kamu!

00:24:16.160 --> 00:24:17.000
Anda...

